oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: UNICEF tour - Australia - 1972 - part 6
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Part six of a 1972 UNICEF fundraiser tour performance of Australia. Featuring Tex Ritter (host/performer).
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Tex Ritter
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dcterms:tableOfContents: (00:00) Reverend Pryor thanks the audience and all the performers, for coming together for UNICEF and Auscare, and describes the situation in Bangladesh -- (01:45) Tex Ritter thanks Pryor, and begins the intermission -- (02:04) [Unidentified] introduces Tex Ritter -- (02:35) Wayward Wind (Tex Ritter) -- (04:20) Tex Ritter talks and introduces the next tune -- (05:23) Deck Of Cards (Tex Ritter) -- (09:07) Ritter thanks the audience and introduces his band -- (09:45) Ritter talks and introduces the next tune -- (10:35) Hillbilly Heaven (Tex Ritter) (incomplete)
